Gregory Alan Williams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gregory_Alan_Williams 0 Gregory Alan Williams (born June 12, 1956) is an American actor and author. He is known for portraying LAPD Officer Garner Ellerbee in Baywatch. From 2011 until 2013, Williams portrayed the role of Coach Pat Purnell in the USA Network series Necessary Roughness. Williams also appeared on the 2015 ABC series Secrets and Lies then on Greenleaf, and in 2017 on Manhunt: Unabomber Gregory_Alan_Williams ( born June_12_,_1956 ) is an_American_actor_and_author .
